@node "Introduction" "Introduction"

    AmTagEd is a program to edit the ID3 TAGs in MPEG audio files.

    It has useful GUI with full keyboard control. There is no need to use this
    program with file manager programs. AmTagEd has own file manager with
    recursive directory handling.
@endnode

