@node "BetterString.mcc" "BetterString.mcc"

                              @{b}BetterString.mcc@{ub}
                          ę 1998 by Allan Odgaard


  BetterString is a stringgadget replacement. It is  created  for @{"áMUIá" link "MUI" 0}, so
  using   it   should  eliminate  the  problems  with  the  original  BOOPSI
  StringClass. The class offers the  user  to  do  number  arithmetic,  like
  increase,  decrease  and BIN<->HEX conversion. It has filename completion,
  ability to mark, cut, copy and paste text - Both via mouse  and  keyboard.
  The length of the contents buffer will dynamically be expanded to hold all
  of what the user type (unless a maximum length is given)

                                Allan Odgaard
                                Dagmarsgade 36
                              DK-2200 Copenhagen
                             EMail : Duff@DIKU.DK

                       http://www.DIKU.DK/students/duff/
@endnode

